'''李·安祖·軒祖'''（{{lang-en|'''Lee Andrew Hendrie'''}}，{{bd|1977年|5月18日}}），已退役的[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[中場|中場]]。他曾為[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]成員以及取得一頂[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭國家隊]]喼帽。

==生平==
===球會===
;阿士東維拉
軒祖出生於[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]，於1995年12月23日首度代表[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]出場，在1:0擊敗[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]一戰中後備入替，於1997/98年球季獲得球會「年度最佳青年球員」獎，更為維拉於2000年[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]決賽披甲。但他的發展減慢了，不斷的[[紅牌|紅牌]]使他於2000年始被雪藏，直至2003年奧拉利的上任，給予他第二個機會。

在2005/06年球季失去維拉的正選席位後，軒祖在[[維拉公園球場|維拉公園球場]]的年代已步入尾聲，[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]則表示對他有興趣。9月29日，他經爸爸的推介，外借至[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]<ref name="qpr0611"/><ref name="bbc5391308">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/5391308.stm|title=Stoke complete Hendrie loan deal|date=29 September 2006|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2007-01-02|archive-date=2006-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061107123445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/5391308.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年1月30日，他和「陶工」的借用期延長至2006/07年球季季尾<ref name="bbc6302681">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6302681.stm|accessdate=2007-06-07|date=30 January 2007|title=Stoke snap up Hendrie and Zakuani|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|archive-date=2014-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140514193202/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6302681.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;錫菲聯
2007年7月19日，軒祖以自由身資格，和[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]簽訂3年合約<ref name="sufc1075620">{{Cite news | url = http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10418~1075620,00.html | title = Blades capture Hendrie | date = 19 July 2007 | publisher = Sheffield United F.C. | accessdate = 2008-05-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090203165221/http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10418~1075620,00.html | archivedate = 2009年2月3日 }}</ref><ref name="bbc6268474">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/6268474.stm |title=Sheff Utd sign midfielder Hendrie |date=19 July 2007 |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |accessdate=2007-07-19 |archive-date=2007-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070907134611/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/6268474.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於聯賽揭幕戰首度在新球會亮相，該場球隊於主場以2:2賽和[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]<ref name="sufc37442">{{Cite news | url = http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10418~37442,00.html | title = Sheffield United v Colchester | date = 11 August 2007 | publisher = Sheffield United F.C. | accessdate = 2008-05-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080512110322/http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10418~37442,00.html | archivedate = 2008年5月12日 }}</ref>。可是，他因受傷而缺席上半球季<ref name="sufc1093444">{{Cite news | url = http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10418~1093444,00.html | title = Hendrie shocker | date = 16 August 2007 | publisher = Sheffield United F.C. | accessdate = 2008-05-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070822225013/http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10418~1093444,00.html | archivedate = 2007年8月22日 }}</ref><ref name="thestar3442594">{{Cite news | title = Blades concentrate on getting Hendrie fit | date = 3 November 2007 | publisher = Sheffield Star | url = http://www.thestar.co.uk/blades/Blades-concentrate-on-getting-Hendrie.3442594.jp | accessdate = 2008-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071112030630/http://www.thestar.co.uk/blades/Blades-concentrate-on-getting-Hendrie.3442594.jp | archive-date = 2007-11-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。軒祖在[[2007年9月|2007年9月]]以5:0大勝[[摩尔甘比足球俱乐部|摩尔甘比]]的[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]賽事中，首次為「刀片」取得入球<ref name="sufc43053">{{Cite news | title = Sheffield Utd v Morecambe - Match Report | date = 25 September 2007 | publisher = Sheffield United F.C. | url = http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10418~43053,00.html | accessdate = 2008-05-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080506094912/http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10418~43053,00.html | archivedate = 2008年5月6日 }}</ref>，但因球會護級的關係，他一直未能站穩正選一席位。

[[2008年2月|2008年2月]]，[[白賴仁·笠臣|白賴仁·笠臣]]離隊，由新教練[[布力維爾|布力維爾]]接任，很快便將軒祖租借於護級的[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]<ref name="sufcmad379589">{{cite news| title=Hendrie to Leicester| url=http://www.sheffieldunited-mad.co.uk/news/loadnews.asp?cid=TMNW&id=379589| publisher=Blades-Mad| date=27 February 2008| accessdate=2008-02-27| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080302191513/http://www.sheffieldunited-mad.co.uk/news/loadnews.asp?cid=TMNW&id=379589| archivedate=2008年3月2日}}</ref>，被視為永久的轉會<ref name="bbc7307747">{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/7307747.stm|title=Hendrie happy to stay with Foxes|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=21 March 2008|accessdate=2008-03-24|archive-date=2008-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080325003537/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/7307747.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2009年3月29日對[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]一戰，一箭定江山<ref name="bbc7309405">{{Cite news | title = Leicester 1-0 Scunthorpe | date = 29 March 2008 | publisher = [[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7309405.stm | accessdate = 2008-05-11 | archive-date = 2008-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080403033713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7309405.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，可惜仍未能助球會護級，其後便返會白馬徑。

2008年11月16日，他以借用形式加盟[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，為期至2009年1月1日<ref name="blackpool switch">{{Cite news | title = Hendrie in loan switch | date = 16 November 2008 | publisher = sufc.co.uk | url = http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10418~1456144,00.html | accessdate = 2008-11-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081222010824/http://www.sufc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10418~1456144,00.html | archivedate = 2008年12月22日 }}</ref>。在同日便首度為新東家上陣，主場迎戰[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]時後備入替。2008年12月9日對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]一仗被逐離場，於2008年12月31日返回錫菲聯，合共上陣6場<ref name="back to blades">{{cite news
