| dead-url = yes
}}</ref>，但他至季尾，只獲得數場後備上陣的機會。

;打比郡
2009年9月1日軒祖以交換球員形式加盟另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[德比郡足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:德比郡;zh-hk:打比郡}-]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5530245,00.html |title=Blades agree swap deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-09-01 |accessdate=2009-09-02 |archive-date=2010-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105054703/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5530245,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於受傷患困擾，軒祖上陣機會不多，於2010年3月23日被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]直到球季結束，如合用更可於夏季正式轉會<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6049824,00.html |title=Seagulls swoop for Hendrie |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-03-23 |accessdate=2010-03-24 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152346/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6049824,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣8場。5月13日打比郡時任領隊[[尼祖·哥洛夫|尼祖·哥洛夫]]（Nigel Clough）表明軒祖在6月約滿後不獲續約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8679598.stm |title=Derby County release Lee Hendrie and Lewis Price |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-05-13 |accessdate=2010-05-14 |archive-date=2010-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100905093647/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8679598.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;巴拉福特
離開打比郡後軒祖一直跟隨[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]操練，但沒有獲得錄用。最終於2010年9月17日以短約形式加盟[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|巴拉福特]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6383033,00.html |title=Hendrie makes Bantams move |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-09-17 |accessdate=2010-09-18 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309133509/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6383033,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於2011年1月2日領隊[[彼得·泰勒|-{zh-hans:彼得·泰勒; zh-hk:彼得·泰萊;}-]]以預算不足為由放棄與他續約，期間上陣12場及射入兩球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/9333558.stm |title=Bradford City release veteran Lee Hendrie |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-02 |accessdate=2011-01-03 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310100331/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bradford_city/9333558.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;萬隆
2011年1月26日軒祖轉戰[[亞洲|亞洲]]球壇，加盟[[印尼超級足球聯賽|印尼超級足球聯賽]]球會[[Bandung_F.C.|萬隆]]（FC Bandung），簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1350989/Lee-Hendrie-swaps-England-Indonesia-Aston-Villa-man-joins-rebel-Asian-league.html |title=Lee Hendrie swaps England for Indonesia as former Aston Villa man joins rebel Asian league |publisher=''dailymail.co.uk'' |date=2011-01-27 |accessdate=2011-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214415/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1350989/Lee-Hendrie-swaps-England-Indonesia-Aston-Villa-man-joins-rebel-Asian-league.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
李·軒祖總共為[[英格蘭U21|英格蘭U21]]上陣12場並攻入5球。<ref name="bbc16359">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/shared/bsp/hi/football/statistics/players/h/hendrie_16359.stm|title=Squad profiles - Lee Hendrie|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2008-11-16|archive-date=2006-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060219112507/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/shared/bsp/hi/football/statistics/players/h/hendrie_16359.stm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在1998年11月18日對戰[[捷克共和國國家足球隊|捷克隊]]的賽事中，他為英格蘭贏得了他唯一的國際賽。

==個人生活==
李·亨德里是由前[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]职业足球运动员[[保罗·亨德里|保罗·亨德里]]（Paul Hendrie）所生。<ref name="qpr0611">{{cite news|url=http://qprreport.blogspot.com/2006/11/lee-hendrie-on-why-he-chose-stoke-over.html|title=Lee Hendrie on why he chose Stoke over QPR|date=16 November 2006|publisher=qprblogspot.com|accessdate=2008-11-16|archive-date=2018-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826214752/http://qprreport.blogspot.com/2006/11/lee-hendrie-on-why-he-chose-stoke-over.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="4thegame27053">{{cite news|url=http://www.4thegame.com/club/avfc/news/27053/HENDRIE+HAILS+DAD&apos%3BS+HELPING+HAND.html|title=Hendrie hails dad's helping hand|date=28 January 1998|publisher=4thegame.com|accessdate=2008-11-16|archive-date=2009-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203182145/http://www.4thegame.com/club/aston-villa-fc/news/27053/HENDRIE+HAILS+DAD%27S+HELPING+HAND.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他是另外一名足球运动员[[约翰·亨德里|约翰·亨德里]]（John Hendrie）的表亲。

2012年1月27日，李·亨德里宣佈破產，期間他兩度嘗試自殺<ref>{{cite web|title=Surge in top-flight footballers facing bankruptcy as film and property investments turn sour|url=http://www.thisismoney.co.uk/money/news/article-2115420/Surge-flight-footballers-facing-bankruptcy-film-property-investments-turn-sour.html?ITO=1490|work=This is Money|accessdate=9 May 2013|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815205156/http://www.thisismoney.co.uk/money/news/article-2115420/Surge-flight-footballers-facing-bankruptcy-film-property-investments-turn-sour.html?ITO=1490|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

